data.description: Welcome to HOME...2427 Gentle Brook Court, a captivating 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath, 2-story home with a saltwater pool in Northfork offering an exquisite blend of modern elegance, timeless comfort, and updates galore. A custom-built Wine Cabinet/Cellar. The kitchen features granite counters, gas stove, pull-out drawers for pots and pans. Oversized primary bedroom has a sitting area and is wired for surround sound. The recently updated primary bath features a separate shower and Whirlpool tub. Custom closets in the primary bathroom & guest room. Guest bathroom remodeled in March 2021. The backyard oasis has a covered patio with travertine floors that overlook a saltwater pool with a waterfall feature. Sprinkler system in front and back yard; lockable metal gates on each side of the house and walking paths. Perfect for entertaining guests or simply enjoying a quiet evening under the stars, this outdoor space is your own private retreat. Clear Creek Schools **HOME IS TENANT OCCUPIED**
